<title>USA: National Penn to split stock 4-for-3.</title>
<headline>National Penn to split stock 4-for-3.</headline>
<dateline>BOYERTOWN, Pa. 1997-06-25</dateline>
<text>
<p>National Penn Bancshares Inc said Wednesday it has approved a split of its common stock, four shares for three.</p>
<p>The company said the split will be effective for shareholders of record on July 15.</p>
<p>The company also declared the third quarter cash dividend of $0.21 per share, payable August 17 to shareholders of record July 31.</p>
<p>The dividend, paid on post-split shares, represents a 16.5 percent annualized increase over the previous dividend of $0.21 per share.</p>
